cus on interesting characters (often one of the most important thing in a fictional piece of work), too much realism, too much black humor and just too much bad boy style in general IMHO. I for one sure don't want that.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent"> implore you all to try one of these modern games you hate so much</div>I wouldn't comment on this if I hadn't played the games.

		

